te have been inconclusive. Glycosaminoglycans contribute to joint cartilage elasticity, strength, and flexibility.[A232144] A systematic review of various studies and guidelines determined that modest improvements were reported for joint pain and function in patients taking glucosamine. A consistent joint space narrowing was observed, but with an unclear clinical significance.[A231894]', 'DrugBank', 0, 0, 0);
